Class DrawnViewComponent

    ComponentListener, AnimationBeanGenerator, DrawingLayerElement, Groupable, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.undo.StateEditable
    public class DrawnViewComponent
extends DrawnComponent
implements Groupable
    A DrawnComponent extension used to render one ViewComponent inside another View. This includes embedded connections and an image.
    See Also:
    DrawnEmbeddedConnection, ViewComponent, Serialized Form
